<style>
  .returns-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--page-padding);
  }

  .returns-page__title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .returns-page h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .returns-page p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .returns-page ul {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .returns-page li {
    list-style: disc;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .returns-page ol {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .returns-page ol li {
    list-style: decimal;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
</style>

<div class="returns-page">
  <h1 class="heading-1 returns-page__title">Returns & Exchanges</h1>

  <h2 class="heading-3">30-Day Return Policy</h2>
  <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If for any reason you are not, you may return your item within 30 days from the date of delivery for a full refund.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Return Conditions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Items must be unworn and in their original condition</li>
    <li>Items must be returned in their original packaging (jewelry box, certificate, polishing cloth)</li>
    <li>Items that show signs of wear, damage, or alteration cannot be accepted</li>
    <li>Sale items are final sale and cannot be returned</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="heading-3">How to Return</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Email <a href="mailto:hello@theclearcut.com.au" style="text-decoration:underline;">hello@theclearcut.com.au</a> with your order number and reason for return</li>
    <li>Our team will provide you with a prepaid return shipping label (Australian orders)</li>
    <li>Pack your item securely in its original packaging</li>
    <li>Drop off at your nearest Australia Post outlet</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Refund Processing</h2>
  <p>Once we receive and inspect your return, your refund will be processed within 5-7 business days to your original payment method. You will receive an email confirmation once your refund has been issued.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Exchanges</h2>
  <p>If you would like to exchange your item for a different size or finish, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@theclearcut.com.au" style="text-decoration:underline;">hello@theclearcut.com.au</a>. We will arrange the exchange and cover the shipping costs for Australian orders.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
  <p>If your item arrives damaged or defective, please contact us immediately with photos of the damage. We will arrange a replacement or full refund at no cost to you. This is covered under our Lifetime Warranty.</p>
</div>

